there and stay there.

00:17:25.126 --> 00:17:27.500
There's boarding provided,
and completely free education.

00:17:27.500 --> 00:17:30.420
And the focus is really
on character building.

00:17:30.420 --> 00:17:32.150
And we're also proud
to say that there

00:17:32.150 --> 00:17:35.270
is specific initiatives being
done for providing education

00:17:35.270 --> 00:17:36.520
to girls.

00:17:36.520 --> 00:17:40.390
