created by God,

01:05:10.190 --> 01:05:12.660
because there's beauty, this
so much, you forget everything

01:05:12.660 --> 01:05:14.230
when you see the beauty.

01:05:14.230 --> 01:05:18.740
And men trying hard to be
listened and take the place.

01:05:18.740 --> 01:05:20.030
It's just a tricky question.

01:05:20.030 --> 01:05:22.370
I don't see that women are less.

01:05:22.370 --> 01:05:25.260
Everywhere, if you see in
rock, pop, [INAUDIBLE],

01:05:25.260 --> 01:05:28.590
there are a lot of women
singing and playing instruments.

01:05:28.590 --> 01:05:31.520
I don't see less women in
here in this profession.

01:05:31.520 --> 01:05:32.830
I mean, that's my opinion.

01:05:32.830 --> 01:05:33.670
I may be wrong.

